---
title: Cherry Tomato, Courgette & Basil Pizza with Pear & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Add extra flavour to your vegetarian pizza by roasting the veggies first to ensure every bite is a tasty delight. Top the whole thing with basil leaves for a fresh and fragrant flavour so you’ll never rely on takeaway again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cherry-tomato-courgette-basil-pizza-5ef6e7e7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/cherry-tomato-courgette-basil-pizza-5fe01193ffbca863e22bca9b-f436d1b2.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/cherry-tomato-courgette-and-basil-pizza-5fe01193ffbca863e22bca9b
